---
import Pill from './Pill.astro';
---

<section id='portfolio' class='flex container min-h-screen my-6 w-full'>
	<div class='flex flex-col gap-8 my-auto p-2 text-center'>
		<div>
			<h2 class='text-4xl font-bold'>Portfolio</h2>
			<p class='text-sm py-1' data-i18n-key='portfolio-subtitle'>
				I have recently started to get back in the market and pursue a new
				position in front-end development. Here are some personal projects that
				I have worked on recently to showcase my skills and learn new things.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class='flex flex-col gap-6'>
			<h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>Dailys board</h3>
			<a href='https://dailys-board.vercel.app/' target='_blank'
				><img
					src={'img/dailys-board-screenshot.jpg'}
					alt='proyecto1'
					class='rounded-lg w-80 mx-auto'
				/></a
			>
			<p class='text-sm' data-i18n-key='dailys-board-description'>
				With remote work we lost the good old analogic board that helped the
				team move the daily meeting forward. Tired of awkward silents and people
				asking who had already talked, I created this simple app to help my
				team. Currently it is using localstorage for data persistency, and I'm
				working on adding a toast notification feature.
			</p>
			<ul class='flex gap-2 text-sm flex-wrap justify-center'>
				<Pill tag={'react'} />
				<Pill tag={'tailwind'} />
				<Pill tag={'cypress'} />
				<Pill tag={'Hooks'} />
			</ul>
			<div class='flex justify-evenly'>
				<a
					class='bg-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-300 dark:bg-sky-800 dark:hover:bg-sky-700 rounded py-3 px-6 border-black border'
					href='https://dailys-board.vercel.app/'
					target='_blank'>
					<span class='font-semibold'>Demo</span></a
				>
				<a
					href='https://github.com/albertocaparros/dailys-board'
					target='_blank'
					class='bg-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-300 dark:bg-sky-800 dark:hover:bg-sky-700 rounded py-3 px-6 border-black border'
					><i class='uil uil-brackets-curly button_icon'></i>
					<span data-i18n-key='code' class='font-semibold'>Code</span></a
				>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class='flex flex-col gap-6'>
			<h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>My travel journal</h3>
			<a href='https://mytrips.vercel.app/' target='_blank'
				><img
					src={'img/my-travel-journal-screenshot.jpg'}
					alt='proyecto 2'
					class='rounded-lg w-80 mx-auto'
				/></a
			>
			<p class='text-sm' data-i18n-key='travel-journal-description'>
				I developed this app to make a little journal where I can keep track of
				the places I have visited over the world. You can check the pictures and
				some information on the locations, as well as seeing all the spots in
				the map. Originally a vanilla js app, I made a second iteration of this
				project using Remix.
			</p>
			<ul class='flex gap-2 text-sm flex-wrap justify-center'>
				<Pill tag={'react'} />
				<Pill tag={'remix'} />
				<Pill tag={'css'} />
				<Pill tag={'prisma'} />
				<Pill tag={'Google Maps API'} />
			</ul>
			<div class='flex justify-evenly'>
				<a
					href='https://mytrips.vercel.app/'
					target='_blank'
					class='bg-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-300 dark:bg-sky-800 dark:hover:bg-sky-700 rounded py-3 px-6 border-black border'>
					<span class='font-semibold'>Demo</span></a
				>
				<a
					href='https://github.com/albertocaparros/mytrips'
					target='_blank'
					class='bg-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-300 dark:bg-sky-800 dark:hover:bg-sky-700 rounded py-3 px-6 border-black border'>
					<span data-i18n-key='code' class='font-semibold'>Code</span></a
				>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
